Package project1

Class Event

java.lang.Object
project1.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Event>
public class Event extends Object implements Comparable<Event>
This class constructs event objects. An event object holds a date, a starting time,a location, contact information, and a duration.
Author:
Micheal Kassie, Donald Yubeaton
